    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/baff3c229f9c6b156950522be6dab89d.avif?t=1769932821\" width=600 height=145 /></span>哲学家们已经在浪费时间和生命思考“思考”这件事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那为什么不在思考的同时享受乐趣呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/00f43c1494f13571f404844137e5d17a.poster.avif?t=1769932821\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/00f43c1494f13571f404844137e5d17a.webm?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/00f43c1494f13571f404844137e5d17a.mp4?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Trolley Solution</strong> 是一款基于1967年由英国哲学家菲利帕·福特提出的著名电车难题的小游戏合集。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/b1097ba16ab9c7cd45e8b344cd94187b.poster.avif?t=1769932821\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/b1097ba16ab9c7cd45e8b344cd94187b.webm?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/b1097ba16ab9c7cd45e8b344cd94187b.mp4?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >测试你的思维能力，在这个问题的幽默变体中选择义务论还是功利主义。解锁各种小游戏，挑战你的游戏技巧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/d8ccfb3daa059203ae9407fb68301719.poster.avif?t=1769932821\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/d8ccfb3daa059203ae9407fb68301719.webm?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/d8ccfb3daa059203ae9407fb68301719.mp4?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战自己，学习重要且有用的哲学知识，同时拓展你的思维！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 20 个电车难题变体（加上原始版本）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 20 个根据每个变体设计的小游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>免责声明：玩这款游戏可能不会让你学到任何有用或重要的知识，也不会拓展你的思维。</i></p>",
